ontent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jwc1665702609865.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jwc1665702609865.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jwc1665702609865.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jwc1665702609865\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Repetition\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the label is repeated when multiple occurrences are drawn. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Do no repeat</code> (default), <code class=\"ph codeph\">Repeat if not empty</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Repeat</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__section_w1840ab1b5b1_w1841ab1b5_w1842ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Do no\n                           repeat</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__2\">Do not repeat the label.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Repeat if not empty</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__2\">Repeat the label if the attached field contains\n                        data.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jwc1665702609865__table_d12974e1_d12975e1_d12976e1__entry__2\">Repeat label for each occurrence of the\n                        entity.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__section_vv4_j2k_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611614e118\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__p_d109940e1_d109941e1_d109942e1\">This property can be set only via the pop-up menu\n            on a label.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jwc1665702609865__section_skf_k2k_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611614e127\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngv1688454370143.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngv1688454370143.html\" title=\"A label displays text on a component, such as the name of an associated field or an instruction to the user.\">Label</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702614021.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Labels in Forms and Reports</a><p>Labels are objects that contain static. Most labels are associated with a field, but unassociated labels can be used for any static text on the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614027\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614027\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Repetition Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Repetition Determines whether the label is repeated when multiple occurrences are drawn. Valid values are Do no repeat (default), Repeat if not empty , or Repeat . Value Description Do no repeat Do not repeat the label. Repeat if not empty Repeat the label if the attached field contains data. Repeat label for each occurrence of the entity. Description This property can be set only via the pop-up menu on a label. Applies To Label Related Links Labels in Forms and Reports Labels are objects that contain static. Most labels are associated with a field, but unassociated labels can be used for any static text on the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}